#  Fix output to imod's qconfigure under RH 8.0
#
#  Revision 3.5.2.6  2003/01/27 00:38:37  mast
#  fine-tuning the build after pure Qt imod
#
#  Revision 3.5.2.5  2002/12/06 22:08:30  mast
